      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "うぅ、もう食べられないよぉ……",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okuyamaliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 6.4429249446
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ん……はっ……ここは……？\n確か、昨日……すみれの実家にお邪魔して……",
      "startTime": 11.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_03-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "あ、{user}さん\nおはようございます。調子はどうですか？",
      "startTime": 18.3607929285,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 166.6666666999994,
          "startTime": 16.395463276
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okuyamaliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 22.7287953378
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_03-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、昨日はついつい私も家族も勧め過ぎちゃって\nすみませんでした",
      "startTime": 28.8287953378,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ちょう、し……？　……あ、思い出した……",
      "startTime": 30.9954620045,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（そう、俺は……）",
      "startTime": 36.6231486639,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "okuyamaliving-00-night",
      "startTime": 40.0984092475
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "okuyamaliving-00-night",
      "startTime": 40.0984092475
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "せっかくの一家団欒なのに\n俺がお邪魔しても良かったのか……？",
      "startTime": 43.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "okuyamaliving-00-night",
      "startTime": 46.0858679217
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_03-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "気にしないで下さい！\nおつまみを準備してあるので、一緒に食べましょう",
      "startTime": 48.0525345883,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "okuyamaliving-00-night",
      "startTime": 51.7858686846
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_03-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "山形の美味しいもの、一杯あるんです\nあ、ほら、テーブルに揃いましたよ～",
      "startTime": 55.419201255,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "凄いご馳走だな。じゃあ、いただきます\n……うまい！　いくらでも食べられそうな味付けだ！",
      "startTime": 66.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "okuyamaliving-00-night",
      "startTime": 69.7440106155
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_03-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "わーっ！　良かった！\nお母さんの料理、どれも美味しいんですよ！",
      "startTime": 72.5440098526,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_03-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "この芋煮もどうぞ召し上がって下さい！",
      "startTime": 76.2440106155,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "okuyamaliving-00-night",
      "startTime": 79.5106772822
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、いただきます\n……おぉ、滋味深い味がする……",
      "startTime": 82.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "okuyamaliving-00-night",
      "startTime": 86.805189713
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_03-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "素材の味が濃いから、薄味でも引き立つんです\n濃い味のおかずが多いので箸休めにいいですよね",
      "startTime": 91.5718556168,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_03-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "こっちは山形の郷土料理で、『だし』っていうんです\n私が作ったんですけど良ければ味見してくれますか？",
      "startTime": 100.6718556168,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "okuyamaliving-00-night",
      "startTime": 105.2718563797
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、もちろんいただくよ\n……うまいなぁ！　すみれは料理が上手だな",
      "startTime": 109.7692827899,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（そう、こんな感じで、作っては並べられる料理を）\n（勧められるままに食べて食べて食べまくって）",
      "startTime": 118.2817672466,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "okuyamaliving-00-night",
      "startTime": 123.5053019288
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "も、もう食えないし動けない……\nでも……全部美味しかったぞ……",
      "startTime": 128.7485827528,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_03-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "お酒は……もう入りませんよね。ごめんなさい\n気付いたら凄い量を食べさせちゃいましたね",
      "startTime": 138.6449390176,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "okuyamaliving-00-night",
      "startTime": 142.5782817605
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_03-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "あの、良かったら少し休んでいって下さい\nお腹一杯で動くのは大変ですし、うちの家族もぜひって",
      "startTime": 146.6449390176,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな、お言葉に甘えて少し休ませてもらうよ……",
      "startTime": 151.9449484272,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "okuyamaliving-00-night",
      "startTime": 156.9989847265
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_03-smr011.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　居間は好きに使って下さい\nゆっくり休んで下さいね",
      "startTime": 160.3020525343,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okuyamaliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 163.2323086503
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okuyamaliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 163.2323086503
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "（と、休んでいるうちに寝てしまって……）\n（そのまま朝になったのか……）",
      "startTime": 167.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_03-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "すまない、泊めてもらった上に\n布団までかけてもらって",
      "startTime": 173.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okuyamaliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 175.6281706257
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_03-smr012.m4a",
      "text": "いえいえ、お母さんも美味しく沢山食べてもらえて\n嬉しいって喜んでました",
      "startTime": 179.994824831,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_03-smr013.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ！　朝ごはんも用意してるので\nぜひ食べていって下さい！",
      "startTime": 185.9281581643,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okuyamaliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 188.061503959
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_03-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "（……お腹は全然空いてないんだけど……断り辛い）",
      "startTime": 188.061503959,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_03-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "で、でも朝ご飯もご厄介になるのはさすがに悪いよ\nそろそろ俺は……",
      "startTime": 198.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okuyamaliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 200.2759646498
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_03-smr014.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、期待して下さいね！\n奥山家は朝ご飯も豪華でボリューミーですから",
      "startTime": 203.6092855218,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_03-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "よ、よーし……一杯食べて、今日も元気に頑張るぞ",
      "startTime": 208.3426313165,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "―― 一時間後",
      "startTime": 215.4850119992,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
